            <div data-seq="274953744" data-index="1" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem">
                <h2 class="t9"><span class="_j_anchor">故宫，最爱那映日蓝天下一抹红色的宫墙</span></h2>
            </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274953931">
            最近热刷《国家宝藏》，被故宫圈粉，其实也早就想带着叮当去感受下古代帝王家的宏大与威严，而河马先生也早就心心念念的想要去故宫拍建筑，所以这次京城的第一个目的地，故宫走起~<br />

        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962822" data-seq="274962862" data-pid="274962822" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962822.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EC/FD/wKgBZ1o4xkiAbz5lAA7lR483iBM42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EC/FD/wKgBZ1o4xkiAbz5lAA7lR483iBM42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962822" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274963807">
            为了赶拍无人的故宫，我们一大早就出发故宫了，蹲守在宫门外，等待8点开门时做第一波闯荡故宫的游客。住在西四，我们直接一站公交到王府井，然后步行过来。寒冬清早的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>和东华门，安静的让你仿佛感受不到它国际大都市的另一个身份，我想，这大概就是故宫千百年来岁月的积淀带给我们后世的馈赠吧。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962823" data-seq="274962863" data-pid="274962823" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962823.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/ED/A1/wKgBZ1o4xpGALYIkABYHllIGBv414.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/ED/A1/wKgBZ1o4xpGALYIkABYHllIGBv414.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962823" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274966007">
            从东华门不能直接进入故宫了，需要绕着宫墙，走到午门，才能进入。这干净笔直的步道，也是当地老百姓锻炼健身的好场所，这才是真正的皇城根儿啊。这里科普一下，故宫城墙四面各设城门一座：南名午门，北称神武门，左右为东华门、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143797.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="西华" target="_blank">西华</a>门，其中午门为参观入口，神武门为参观出口。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962824" data-seq="274962864" data-pid="274962824" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962824.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/ED/EE/wKgBZ1o4xr2AUQfaAA6wEWoQQCg92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/ED/EE/wKgBZ1o4xr2AUQfaAA6wEWoQQCg92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962824" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274967923">
            光影正好，看树杈的影子映在砖红色的宫墙上，好美！
        </p>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274967906">
            光影正好，看树杈的影子映在
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962825" data-seq="274962865" data-pid="274962825" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962825.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EE/25/wKgBZ1o4xtyAObeXAAnwiWZj2Oo96.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EE/25/wKgBZ1o4xtyAObeXAAnwiWZj2Oo96.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962825" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274968155">
            穿过这道门，就是故宫了。从这里看过去，已感受到了那千年皇宫的霸主威严。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962826" data-seq="274962866" data-pid="274962826" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962826.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EE/5A/wKgBZ1o4xveAK3lRAAjHCqjH9lg69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EE/5A/wKgBZ1o4xveAK3lRAAjHCqjH9lg69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962826" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962827" data-seq="274962867" data-pid="274962827" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962827.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EE/B1/wKgBZ1o4xx-AdffzAAsKK-B8ZJo80.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EE/B1/wKgBZ1o4xx-AdffzAAsKK-B8ZJo80.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962827" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274973296">
            赶着一开门就冲了进去，空无一人的<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143521.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="太和" target="_blank">太和</a>门，震撼，威严。在金水桥上来一张游客照，纪念叮当的第一次故宫之行。金水桥共5座，单孔拱券式。广场南部自西向东蜿蜒流淌着一条如弓形的金水河，这就是所谓的“内金水桥”。这是紫禁城内最大，也是最壮观，最华美的一组石桥。正中的是御路桥，供皇帝专用。东西两侧为王公桥，供皇室成员、亲王大臣通行。再两侧为品级桥，供三品以上官员行走。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962828" data-seq="274962868" data-pid="274962828" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962828.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EE/F7/wKgBZ1o4x0KALCTTAAw13tNMGck89.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EE/F7/wKgBZ1o4x0KALCTTAAw13tNMGck89.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962828" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274976268">
            从午门进来，沿着中轴线行走，我们最先迎来的就是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143521.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="太和" target="_blank">太和</a>门，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143521.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="太和" target="_blank">太和</a>门是紫禁城内最大的宫门，也是外朝宫殿的正门。最吸引人的是<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143521.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="太和" target="_blank">太和</a>门前的那一对铜狮，雕工细致，栩栩如生。这一对铜狮霸气、威严，象征着皇权的无上尊贵。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962829" data-seq="274962869" data-pid="274962829" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962829.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EF/34/wKgBZ1o4x1yASdkMAAht6AZ4p4I98.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EF/34/wKgBZ1o4x1yASdkMAAht6AZ4p4I98.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962829" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962830" data-seq="274962870" data-pid="274962830" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962830.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EF/70/wKgBZ1o4x3aAfCuLAAe7cpO7klY30.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EF/70/wKgBZ1o4x3aAfCuLAAe7cpO7klY30.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962830" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274977269">
            故宫的布局很<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143809.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="方正" target="_blank">方正</a>，横平竖直&nbsp;，以<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143521.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="太和" target="_blank">太和</a>殿、中和殿、保和殿所在的中轴线前后左右延伸开来，当游客们的兴趣点都集中在中轴线上的时候，避开人流，从中轴线两侧的偏殿拍起，皇家宫殿的壮美威严一览无余，这里要手动给河马先生打电话了<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/28@2x.png" style="width:23px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962831" data-seq="274962871" data-pid="274962831" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962831.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EF/AF/wKgBZ1o4x5uAAOTdAAtbTnxQ3WA14.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EF/AF/wKgBZ1o4x5uAAOTdAAtbTnxQ3WA14.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962831" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274978967">
            小小的人儿漫步于偌大的紫禁城，影子被拉的好长好长，爱极了这幅画面。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962832" data-seq="274962872" data-pid="274962832" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962832.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EF/CD/wKgBZ1o4x6qAAtXZAAQiCDZjCcA28.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EF/CD/wKgBZ1o4x6qAAtXZAAQiCDZjCcA28.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962832" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="274981257">
            小朋友就是活力无限。为了赶着8点开门就进场，大早晨的把他从温暖的被窝里揪起来，看着他一脸懵逼的样子还觉得有点对不住他，可到了故宫，他已然恢复了平日欢实的样子，在偌大的故宫内，攀着楼梯，爬上爬下，一副活力无限的小模样。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962833" data-seq="274962873" data-pid="274962833" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962833.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EF/F2/wKgBZ1o4x7qAOtMgAANIWrNCq6E02.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/EF/F2/wKgBZ1o4x7qAOtMgAANIWrNCq6E02.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962833" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="275080274">
            当妈4年，我最骄傲的一件事，就是刚刚满4岁的叮当小朋友超级爱国，热爱八路军，热爱共产党，所以当故宫门口有卖国旗的时候，他不要玩具也要买一只国旗带进故宫来。历久弥新，我大中华的文化在传承，剪不断的是那一颗爱国的赤子心<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/21@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962834" data-seq="274962874" data-pid="274962834" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962834.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F0/10/wKgBZ1o4x8WAF5zRAAQAmGxsf7o34.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F0/10/wKgBZ1o4x8WAF5zRAAQAmGxsf7o34.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962834" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="275080917">
            悄悄的坐在大殿的台阶上，张望壮美与神秘的紫禁城。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962835" data-seq="274962875" data-pid="274962835" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
