            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F0/42/wKgBZ1o4x9eAcq4dAARi69v3_nQ82.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F0/42/wKgBZ1o4x9eAcq4dAARi69v3_nQ82.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962835" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="275081098">
            低头，又是在想什么呢？
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962836" data-seq="274962876" data-pid="274962836" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962836.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:382px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F0/5F/wKgBZ1o4x-aAdw2_AARPF06I_ek60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F0/5F/wKgBZ1o4x-aAdw2_AARPF06I_ek60.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962836" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="275081143">
            注意！！！这是此行蝈蝈小姐在故宫唯一留下的一张人像，你们且行且珍惜的看吧<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v3/37@2x.png" style="width:28px;" />为啥捏~原来我们去那天赶上了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>难得一遇的八级大风，等我回来才后知后觉的收到短信，都橙色预警了！！！！所以在空旷的大故宫吹了半小时我感觉自己都快无法思考了，怕把叮当再给吹病了，于是果断的做了个决定——我带着叮当先撤了，留下河马先生继续拍拍拍，也不枉我们不畏狂风的走一遭。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962837" data-seq="274962877" data-pid="274962837" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962837.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F0/9F/wKgBZ1o4yA6ARQbvAAvC8Km__Ps90.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F0/9F/wKgBZ1o4yA6ARQbvAAvC8Km__Ps90.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962837" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="275083082">
            于是，叮当人生第一次的故宫之行就在八级大风的猛烈鼓吹下宣告结束了。在他小小的脑海里，大概只记住了这是曾经皇帝住过的地方吧，扎心~~~~不过来日方长，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143521.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="太和" target="_blank">太和</a>殿，等着我们再来与你赴下一个守望之约！
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962838" data-seq="274962878" data-pid="274962838" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962838.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F0/CB/wKgBZ1o4yC2AEUF2AAo1VYh8J3U95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F0/CB/wKgBZ1o4yC2AEUF2AAo1VYh8J3U95.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962838" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="275086847">
            接下来是河马先生自己漫无目的走走逛逛的片子，虽然没办法详细的介绍所到之处的典籍、感受，但回来看到这些片子，心中升腾的，也是浓浓的感动。八级大风吹跑了我们，却也吹出了<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>蓝。红色的宫墙、黄色的琉璃瓦，在濯濯蓝天下泛着光，这大概就是皇家独有的魅力所在吧。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962839" data-seq="274962879" data-pid="274962839" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962839.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F0/E6/wKgBZ1o4yEKAPlExAAcitFHpkps48.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F0/E6/wKgBZ1o4yEKAPlExAAcitFHpkps48.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962839" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="275093398">
            龙生九子，六子赑屃好负重，通常被创作运用于碑石之下，但<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143521.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="太和" target="_blank">太和</a>殿前的赑屃摆脱了负重，昂首前望，象征着皇权的至高无上，在这里，你的肩膀上，没有束缚。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962840" data-seq="274962880" data-pid="274962840" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962840.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F1/10/wKgBZ1o4yF6AJZazAAh_Ij8bxCs24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F1/10/wKgBZ1o4yF6AJZazAAh_Ij8bxCs24.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962840" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="275094483">
            仙鹤，在古代有着长命百岁、福寿绵长的寓意，同时也在道家里有着极其重要的地位。<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/143521.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="太和" target="_blank">太和</a>殿前的铜龟望鹤，寓皇权永驻、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/12393.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="江山" target="_blank">江山</a>百年之意，同时也彰显统治者海纳百川，尊重各家学派的包容之心。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962841" data-seq="274962881" data-pid="274962841" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962841.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F1/24/wKgBZ1o4yG-AUFZyAAXi84FUGmI53.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F1/24/wKgBZ1o4yG-AUFZyAAXi84FUGmI53.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962841" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="275095885">
            天气清朗，金灿灿的琉璃瓦，几只殿角跑兽仿佛也活了起来。
        </p>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962842" data-seq="274962882" data-pid="274962842" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962842.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F1/48/wKgBZ1o4yIiAEMo6AAlXf5QDXAk42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F1/48/wKgBZ1o4yIiAEMo6AAlXf5QDXAk42.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962842" alt="" />
        </a>
