                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962843" data-seq="274962883" data-pid="274962843" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962843.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F1/6A/wKgBZ1o4yJ-AFe-BAAjur-C3-Jk56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F1/6A/wKgBZ1o4yJ-AFe-BAAjur-C3-Jk56.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962843" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <div id="_j_photo_274962844" data-seq="274962884" data-pid="274962844" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem"  style="width:680px" data-poiid="3474">
        <a target="_blank" style="display: block" href="/photo/10065/scenery_8099659/274962844.html">
            <img class="_j_lazyload _j_needInitShare" style="height:453px;width:680px;background:#FCF2DC" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" data-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F1/8B/wKgBZ1o4yLaADiL1AAktpxVAKQY03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-rt-src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F1/8B/wKgBZ1o4yLaADiL1AAktpxVAKQY03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F1360%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90" data-pid="274962844" alt="" />
        </a>
                                        <span class="pic_tag">
                <a href="/poi/3474.html" class="_j_anchor" data-poiid="3474" target="_blank" data-cs-p="ginfo_img_poi_new">
                    <i class="house"></i>故宫
                </a>
            </span>
                        </div>
            <p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" data-seq="275098397">
            紫禁城，作为明清两代的皇宫，是我国现存最大最完整的古建筑群。是世界上现存规模最大、保存最为完整的木质结构的宫殿型建筑。入选世界文化遗产，力压欧美，强势位列世界五大宫之首，<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10065.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="北京" target="_blank">北京</a>故宫、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10171.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="法国" target="_blank">法国</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/66863.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="凡尔赛" target="_blank">凡尔赛</a>宫、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10122.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="英国" target="_blank">英国</a><a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/100486.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="白金汉" target="_blank">白金汉</a>宫、<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10062.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="美国" target="_blank">美国</a>白宫和<a href="/travel-scenic-spot/mafengwo/10300.html" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" data-kw="俄罗斯" target="_blank">俄罗斯</a>克里姆林宫。<br />
故宫的建筑群，作为古代帝王宫殿中的巅峰之作；它的一切无不体现着天朝大国的气派景象。放眼望去，横平竖直，讲究对称，无一不体现着五百多年前匠师们在建筑上的卓越成就。宏伟壮观、大气磅礴，这些词，都是为了故宫而生的吧。
        </p>
